fetchBalance.description: Query for balance and get the amount of funds available for trading or funds locked in orders

fetchClosedOrders.description: Fetches a list of closed (or canceled) orders

fetchCurrencies.description: Fetches all available currencies on an exchange

fetchDeposits.description: Fetch all deposits made to an account

fetchMarkets.description: Retrieves data on all markets for cube

fetchMyTrades.description: Fetch all trades made by the user

fetchOpenOrders.description: Fetch all unfilled currently open orders

fetchOrder.description: Fetches information on an order made by the user

fetchStatus.description: The latest known information on the availability of the exchange API

fetchTicker.description: Fetches a price ticker, a statistical calculation with the information calculated over the past 24 hours for a specific market

fetchTrades.description: Get the list of most recent trades for a particular symbol

fetchTradingFee.description: Fetch the trading fees for a market

fetchWithdrawals.description: Fetch all withdrawals made from an account
